The ANC is celebrating its 109th anniversary differently this year. Their massive annual event has been cancelled due to the COVID-19 pandemic. President Cyril Ramaphosa will tonight delivery the January 8 statement virtually. * Editor's note: Livestream above courtesy #DStv403. JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa will deliver the ANC's January 8 statement at 7pm. The ANC is marking its 109th anniversary. Their massive annual event has been cancelled due to the COVID-19 pandemic.